## ğŸ¨ Code Style Rules

### Imports
```typescript
// Group imports by type
import { Component } from '@shared/ui/Component';
import { formatPrice } from '@shared/lib/formatPrice';
import type { CartItem, CartResponse } from '@shared/types/api';

